data.description: Beautifully updated and expanded rambler in desirable Broyhill Crest! Custom kitchen with shaker cabinets, quartz countertops, and designer backsplash. Open floor plan is perfect for families or hosting gatherings! Upstairs primary and family area have been freshly painted. Four bedrooms with 3 bathrooms on the main level. Beautiful primary bedroom and bathroom with duel vanity, spa-like shower, separate toilet, and spacious walk-in closet. Fully completed lower level includes a large bonus room, office space, powder bath, with large utility room. Backyard is fully fenced in and ready to create your own space! Convenient location for commuters with its proximity to 495 and 395. Local parks and hiking trails are within walking distance for outdoor recreation! Popular Mosaic District is only a short ten-minute drive.
